1216
00:59:28,031 --> 00:59:29,732
Huh?

1217
00:59:31,668 --> 00:59:33,269
ANGELO:
You think he's followin' us?

1218
00:59:33,336 --> 00:59:34,871
Make a right.

1219
00:59:34,938 --> 00:59:37,206
[TIRES SCREECH]
[HORN HONKS]

1220
00:59:44,747 --> 00:59:46,316
[♪♪♪]

1221
00:59:46,382 --> 00:59:48,885
Oh, shit.

1222
00:59:48,952 --> 00:59:51,854
Are we racin'?
No, everything's fine, kid.

1223
00:59:51,921 --> 00:59:54,624
Just take it easy,
all right?

1224
00:59:54,691 --> 00:59:56,025
[TRUCK HORN HONKS]

1225
00:59:56,092 --> 00:59:57,160
Wow!

1226
00:59:57,226 --> 01:00:00,029
[TIRES SCREECH]
[ENGINE REVS]

1227
01:00:03,366 --> 01:00:05,835
[♪♪♪]

1228
01:00:17,647 --> 01:00:19,782
Ange, that's water.
Water, Ange!

1229
01:00:19,849 --> 01:00:22,652
[♪♪♪]

1230
01:00:32,395 --> 01:00:33,930
Aah!
[GRUNTS]

1231
01:00:33,997 --> 01:00:36,432
RUDY: Son of a bitch!
CARMINE: Somebody's shooting.

1232
01:00:36,499 --> 01:00:38,201
[TIRES SCREECH]

1233
01:00:44,073 --> 01:00:45,675
[GUNSHOT]
Aah!

1234
01:00:45,742 --> 01:00:47,610
Jesus!

1235
01:00:47,677 --> 01:00:50,279
RUDY:
What's the matter with those
guys? We got a kid in here.

1236
01:00:50,346 --> 01:00:52,048
CHARLIE:
Are those guys friends of his?

1237
01:00:52,115 --> 01:00:55,785
RUDY:
Yeah, friends and relatives.

1238
01:00:55,852 --> 01:00:57,587
Hey, where are you going?

1239
01:00:57,653 --> 01:00:59,922
Hey! Hey!

1240
01:00:59,989 --> 01:01:01,958
You recognize this kid?

1241
01:01:02,025 --> 01:01:04,093
I'll throw him
out of the car right now!

1242
01:01:04,160 --> 01:01:06,629
Turn it around!
Turn it around!

1243
01:01:06,696 --> 01:01:09,799
[TIRES SCREECH]

1244
01:01:13,736 --> 01:01:16,539
Good job, kid.
Looks like you scared them away.

1245
01:01:16,606 --> 01:01:18,241
I want to go home.

1246
01:01:18,307 --> 01:01:20,276
Hey.

1247
01:01:20,343 --> 01:01:21,611
Not having fun yet?

1248
01:01:21,677 --> 01:01:23,713
Uh-uh.

1249
01:01:25,081 --> 01:01:27,717
Is that your airplane?

1250
01:01:29,452 --> 01:01:30,686
It's nice.

1251
01:01:30,753 --> 01:01:32,522
I built it.

1252
01:01:32,588 --> 01:01:35,792
You built it yourself? Wow.

1253
01:01:35,858 --> 01:01:37,593
What sort of plane is it?

1254
01:01:37,660 --> 01:01:39,462
It's a SPAD XIII.

1255
01:01:39,529 --> 01:01:41,230
A SPAD XIII.

1256
01:01:41,297 --> 01:01:44,000
Yeah, it's from--
It's from World War I.

1257
01:01:44,067 --> 01:01:45,168
Oh.

1258
01:01:45,234 --> 01:01:47,737
They used it to shoot down
all the Germans.

1259
01:01:47,804 --> 01:01:49,572
That's really nice.

1260
01:01:49,639 --> 01:01:51,074
It's French.

1261
01:01:54,577 --> 01:01:56,979
Let me see that.

1262
01:02:00,349 --> 01:02:02,385
That's beautiful.

1263
01:02:02,452 --> 01:02:03,753
[SIGHS]

1264
01:02:03,820 --> 01:02:06,189
Where are we going?

1265
01:02:07,890 --> 01:02:10,793
We're gonna take you
someplace real special.

1266
01:02:12,128 --> 01:02:14,497
Are you kidnapping me?

1267
01:02:14,564 --> 01:02:17,066
Me? No.

1268
01:02:17,133 --> 01:02:20,103
Why would you say
something like that?

1269
01:02:20,169 --> 01:02:23,506
Hey, Ange, tell the kid
where we're going.

1270
01:02:23,573 --> 01:02:26,509
We're, uh, going to your dad's
summer house.

1271
01:02:26,576 --> 01:02:28,411
Is my mom
gonna be there?

1272
01:02:28,478 --> 01:02:29,745
Uh, yeah.

1273
01:02:29,812 --> 01:02:31,380
Your-- Your mom's
gonna be there.

1274
01:02:31,447 --> 01:02:33,149
I mean, everybody's
gonna be there.

1275
01:02:33,216 --> 01:02:36,252
Maybe not when we arrive,
but they'll be there.

1276
01:02:36,319 --> 01:02:38,020
They'll be there.

1277
01:02:38,087 --> 01:02:40,189
You have my word on that.

1278
01:02:43,059 --> 01:02:45,928
[♪♪♪]

1279
01:03:42,418 --> 01:03:47,023
I'll go in the house with you.
These guys wanna wait out here.

1280
01:03:52,862 --> 01:03:55,464
[WHISTLES]

1281
01:04:02,838 --> 01:04:04,507
[ALARM BEEPS]

1282
01:04:04,574 --> 01:04:06,509
[ALARM BLARES LOUDLY]

1283
01:04:11,147 --> 01:04:13,082
Oh.

1284
01:04:23,726 --> 01:04:25,628
Nice place.

1285
01:04:25,695 --> 01:04:29,131
I cannot believe you're gonna
let this happen. Huh?

1286
01:04:29,198 --> 01:04:32,001
We do this, what's it gonna be
tomorrow? It's gonna get worse.

1287
01:04:32,068 --> 01:04:34,203
How far down are you
gonna let us get

1288
01:04:34,270 --> 01:04:36,205
before you do something here?
What? Huh?

1289
01:04:36,272 --> 01:04:38,941
Will you shut your goddamn
mouth? This isn't my fault.

1290
01:04:39,008 --> 01:04:40,643
I'm not the one
making this happen.

1291
01:04:40,710 --> 01:04:41,978
This wasn't my idea.

1292
01:04:42,044 --> 01:04:44,647
You're the one
letting it happen.

1293
01:04:44,714 --> 01:04:46,649
[CHARLIE WHISTLING]

1294
01:04:53,522 --> 01:04:54,924
You want a soda?

1295
01:04:54,991 --> 01:04:57,860
Huh? Um, no.

1296
01:04:57,927 --> 01:04:59,996
No, thanks.

1297
01:05:04,734 --> 01:05:06,602
[EXCLAIMS AND GASPS]

1298
01:05:11,941 --> 01:05:13,342
What's that?

1299
01:05:13,409 --> 01:05:15,678
Huh?

1300
01:05:15,745 --> 01:05:17,313
That right there.

1301
01:05:17,380 --> 01:05:18,648
Gun.

1302
01:05:18,714 --> 01:05:21,384
You better not let my mom
see that. She hates guns.

1303
01:05:21,450 --> 01:05:25,421
Well, I'll try to be
real careful about that.

1304
01:05:25,488 --> 01:05:28,824
Oh, here's one.

1305
01:05:28,891 --> 01:05:31,494
Oh, thanks.

1306
01:05:34,230 --> 01:05:35,731
Why do you have it?

1307
01:05:35,798 --> 01:05:37,333
[BULLETS RATTLE]

1308
01:05:37,400 --> 01:05:38,534
What?

1309
01:05:38,601 --> 01:05:40,336
For what?

1310
01:05:40,403 --> 01:05:43,806
Um, uh...

1311
01:05:43,873 --> 01:05:45,141
I gotta shoot you, kid.

1312
01:05:45,207 --> 01:05:47,543
No, you don't.

1313
01:05:47,610 --> 01:05:49,712
Yeah, I do.

1314
01:05:49,779 --> 01:05:52,348
Does this still work?

1315
01:05:52,415 --> 01:05:53,549
[SNAPS]

1316
01:05:53,616 --> 01:05:55,785
Thing's ancient.

1317
01:05:55,851 --> 01:05:57,320
The serial number's off.

1318
01:05:57,386 --> 01:06:02,124
A couple of-- This is bent.
Oh, that's great.

1319
01:06:05,828 --> 01:06:07,029
What'd I do?

1320
01:06:07,096 --> 01:06:08,831
Fucking relic. What?

1321
01:06:08,898 --> 01:06:10,733
[CLICKS] Um...

1322
01:06:15,671 --> 01:06:17,673
I don't know.

1323
01:06:17,740 --> 01:06:20,109
[RACKS GUN]

1324
01:06:21,077 --> 01:06:22,545
Sit down.

1325
01:06:27,416 --> 01:06:29,051
Ah...

1326
01:06:29,118 --> 01:06:31,220
Oh, Jesus.

1327
01:06:33,522 --> 01:06:34,757
Hey, kid!

1328
01:06:34,824 --> 01:06:36,926
I don't know.
After this,

1329
01:06:36,992 --> 01:06:38,694
I gotta rethink
some things.

1330
01:06:38,761 --> 01:06:40,496
Rudy, come on.

1331
01:06:43,466 --> 01:06:45,401
Look at you. You're sweating.
You're shaking.

1332
01:06:45,468 --> 01:06:47,336
You don't want this,
but you're too chicken.

1333
01:06:47,403 --> 01:06:48,704
What do you want from me?

1334
01:06:48,771 --> 01:06:50,873
If we don't do the kid,
I gotta do my dad!

1335
01:06:50,940 --> 01:06:52,775
He's an old man, Ange.

1336
01:06:52,842 --> 01:06:54,643
CHARLIE:
Kid!

1337
01:06:56,645 --> 01:06:59,148
Kid.

1338
01:06:59,215 --> 01:07:01,117
Oh, please, don't do this.

1339
01:07:01,183 --> 01:07:02,952
Well, I can't do this one
for you, Ange.

1340
01:07:03,019 --> 01:07:05,421
It's your choice.

1341
01:07:05,488 --> 01:07:07,256
You know?

1342
01:07:10,593 --> 01:07:12,461
[SIGHS]

1343
01:07:18,501 --> 01:07:20,202
Kid.

1344
01:07:20,269 --> 01:07:23,072
I'm gonna find you.

1345
01:07:24,640 --> 01:07:27,109
[GROANS]

1346
01:07:41,023 --> 01:07:42,625
Ha!

1347
01:08:02,511 --> 01:08:03,646
Hey...

1348
01:08:05,347 --> 01:08:06,782
[GLASS SHATTERS]

1349
01:08:14,657 --> 01:08:16,692
Shoot.

1350
01:08:18,861 --> 01:08:20,696
[GRUNTS]

1351
01:08:31,273 --> 01:08:34,310
[RATTLES DOORKNOB]

1352
01:08:36,545 --> 01:08:39,215
How did I get
this stuck?

1353
01:08:54,897 --> 01:08:57,633
[CARMINE PANTING]

1354
01:08:59,101 --> 01:09:01,203
Uh...

1355
01:09:05,941 --> 01:09:07,810
I'm sorry, Rudy.

1356
01:09:12,748 --> 01:09:15,684
Ow! Oh! Ow!
Kid, cut it out.

1357
01:09:15,751 --> 01:09:18,487
Kid! Oh, kid.

1358
01:09:18,554 --> 01:09:20,156
Jesus Christ,
cut it out!

1359
01:09:20,222 --> 01:09:24,160
Please, please, please,
please, please!

1360
01:09:24,226 --> 01:09:25,427
Let go of my leg.

1361
01:09:25,494 --> 01:09:27,162
No!
Let go!

1362
01:09:27,229 --> 01:09:29,899
No!

1363
01:09:29,965 --> 01:09:33,769
No!

1364
01:09:33,836 --> 01:09:36,539
No!

1365
01:09:36,605 --> 01:09:39,842
No, no, no, no,
no, no, no, no, no!

1366
01:09:39,909 --> 01:09:41,677
No.

1367
01:09:45,147 --> 01:09:46,549
Do that again.

1368
01:09:46,615 --> 01:09:48,083
Huh?

1369
01:09:48,150 --> 01:09:49,451
My leg.

1370
01:09:49,518 --> 01:09:53,422
Grab my leg and--
And say, "No, no, no."

1371
01:09:55,357 --> 01:09:58,627
No, no, no, no, no,
no, no, no!

1372
01:10:00,129 --> 01:10:03,199
No!

1373
01:10:03,265 --> 01:10:06,502
No!

1374
01:10:08,137 --> 01:10:10,306
[♪♪♪]

1375
01:10:12,208 --> 01:10:14,743
[CRIES SOFTLY]

1376
01:10:23,919 --> 01:10:25,888
Holy cow.

1377
01:10:28,757 --> 01:10:29,892
[SIGHS]

1378
01:10:40,202 --> 01:10:43,472
Ooh. Ooh.

1379
01:10:48,177 --> 01:10:50,713
Look at that.

1380
01:10:50,779 --> 01:10:52,881
[SIGHS]

1381
01:10:52,948 --> 01:10:54,216
Thank you.

1382
01:10:54,283 --> 01:10:55,584
Thank you.

1383
01:10:55,651 --> 01:10:58,320
Oh, God, kid, thank you,
thank you, thank you.

1384
01:10:58,387 --> 01:10:59,855
[CHUCKLES]

1385
01:10:59,922 --> 01:11:01,624
Ooh, you're so cute.

1386
01:11:01,690 --> 01:11:03,292
[LAUGHS]

1387
01:11:17,306 --> 01:11:19,441
[♪♪♪]

1388
01:11:30,519 --> 01:11:32,521
Holy cow. Holy--

1389
01:11:32,588 --> 01:11:34,023
Ange, thanks.
I mean, this is great.

1390
01:11:34,089 --> 01:11:37,860
I feel so good. I mean,
I had an experience now.

1391
01:11:37,926 --> 01:11:39,261
Unbelievable.

1392
01:11:39,328 --> 01:11:41,430
That I don't even
want the money.

1393
01:11:41,497 --> 01:11:44,233
I just feel so-- Holy cow.

1394
01:11:44,299 --> 01:11:45,734
I feel...

1395
01:11:45,801 --> 01:11:48,537
I feel. I feel.
I gotta-- I gotta--

1396
01:11:48,604 --> 01:11:51,040
I gotta see my doctor.
I gotta go back to the hospital.

1397
01:11:51,106 --> 01:11:52,608
I gotta share.

1398
01:11:52,675 --> 01:11:54,910
Oh, boy.

1399
01:11:58,313 --> 01:11:59,848
That ain't good.

1400
01:12:06,255 --> 01:12:08,223
Rudy, he's alive!

1401
01:12:08,290 --> 01:12:09,525
Yeah, yeah.
I see that, Ange.

1402
01:12:09,591 --> 01:12:11,093
That's great.
Yeah, it's great.

1403
01:12:11,160 --> 01:12:12,294
He's got the gun.

1404
01:12:12,361 --> 01:12:15,397
Yeah, well,
that's the downside.

1405
01:12:18,167 --> 01:12:20,369
ANGELO:
What the hell are we
gonna do now?

1406
01:12:20,436 --> 01:12:21,970
I don't know.
Why are you asking me?

1407
01:12:22,037 --> 01:12:23,572
Hey, should we make
a run for it?

1408
01:12:23,639 --> 01:12:25,307
Into those trees
over there?

1409
01:12:25,374 --> 01:12:26,675
Yeah.
I don't know. Looks dicey.

1410
01:12:26,742 --> 01:12:28,377
Got a better idea?
Not really.

1411
01:12:28,444 --> 01:12:30,312
It beats sitting around
waiting to get shot.

1412
01:12:30,379 --> 01:12:31,513
You got a good point, Ange.

1413
01:12:31,580 --> 01:12:33,315
Okay, on the count of three.
Ready? One--

1414
01:12:33,382 --> 01:12:34,583
Ange. Ange.
Two-- What?

1415
01:12:34,650 --> 01:12:36,552
Ange, Ange.
What?

1416
01:12:36,618 --> 01:12:38,787
All right, kid.

1417
01:12:38,854 --> 01:12:40,322
Here's what
we're gonna do.

1418
01:12:40,389 --> 01:12:41,657
The chasing part was fun,

1419
01:12:41,724 --> 01:12:43,058
but why don't we put
the gun down now

1420
01:12:43,125 --> 01:12:45,127
and we'll just go home?
How about that?

1421
01:12:45,194 --> 01:12:47,529
Put the cannon on the ground
and we'll put it in the car

1422
01:12:47,596 --> 01:12:48,897
and we'll--
It's all over now.

1423
01:12:48,964 --> 01:12:50,666
No, don't shoot!
Don't shoot, Carmine.

1424
01:12:50,733 --> 01:12:52,735
It's okay. It's okay.

1425
01:12:52,801 --> 01:12:55,671
It's-- It's okay.
Just stop. Stop.

1426
01:12:55,738 --> 01:12:57,306
Just stop.
You don't have to shoot.

1427
01:12:57,373 --> 01:13:00,109
Just don't. Don't!

1428
01:13:00,175 --> 01:13:01,510
[BOTH GRUNT]

1429
01:13:01,577 --> 01:13:03,011
CARMINE:
Give me it.

1430
01:13:03,078 --> 01:13:04,413
[GRUNTS]

1431
01:13:07,483 --> 01:13:09,218
Hey, Rudy.

1432
01:13:09,284 --> 01:13:13,889
Hey, that's the first time
I've-- I've faced down a gun.

1433
01:13:13,956 --> 01:13:15,991
I guess I ain't
such a chicken--

1434
01:13:18,961 --> 01:13:20,129
Rudy?

1435
01:13:32,508 --> 01:13:34,343
Rudy.

1436
01:13:34,410 --> 01:13:35,978
Rudy.

1437
01:13:36,044 --> 01:13:37,713
Hey, Rudy.

1438
01:13:37,780 --> 01:13:39,681
[CRIES]

1439
01:13:46,121 --> 01:13:49,558
Rudy, come on.
Don't-- Don't do this.

1440
01:13:49,625 --> 01:13:51,660
[CRIES SOFTLY]

1441
01:14:10,579 --> 01:14:12,948
He's dead.

1442
01:14:14,883 --> 01:14:18,554
I was talking to him
10 seconds ago.

1443
01:14:22,958 --> 01:14:25,127
Rudy.

1444
01:14:27,196 --> 01:14:29,832
Oh, Rudy.

1445
01:14:29,898 --> 01:14:32,000
What do you want me to do
with the kid?

1446
01:14:34,036 --> 01:14:36,672
Take him back.
Take him home.

1447
01:14:36,738 --> 01:14:38,874
Go on, get out of here!

1448
01:14:54,056 --> 01:14:58,093
Oh, Rudy, you're bleeding
all over your...

1449
01:14:58,160 --> 01:15:00,596
Got it on your shirt.

1450
01:15:00,662 --> 01:15:03,699
[CAR DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES]

1451
01:15:09,104 --> 01:15:10,939
Put on your belt.

1452
01:15:17,279 --> 01:15:18,714
[ENGINE STARTS]

1453
01:15:18,780 --> 01:15:20,949
Do you know
how to drive?

1454
01:15:29,424 --> 01:15:32,294
[♪♪♪]

1455
01:15:42,204 --> 01:15:44,006
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

1456
01:15:46,942 --> 01:15:48,977
[KNOCKING CONTINUES]

1457
01:16:03,225 --> 01:16:04,960
Ange?

1458
01:16:08,597 --> 01:16:11,667
ANGELO:
I took it from him
and then it went off,

1459
01:16:11,733 --> 01:16:14,269
and I was laughing.
I said, "Rudy..."

1460
01:16:14,336 --> 01:16:16,905
[CHUCKLES]

1461
01:16:16,972 --> 01:16:20,075
But when I turned around,
he...

1462
01:16:20,142 --> 01:16:23,178
he was laying
on the ground, and...

1463
01:16:26,114 --> 01:16:29,718
I didn't get a chance
to say goodbye.

1464
01:16:32,354 --> 01:16:33,789
Mary.

1465
01:16:33,855 --> 01:16:36,058
Is there a problem here?
Go home, Harry.

1466
01:16:36,124 --> 01:16:37,292
[SIGHS]

1467
01:16:37,359 --> 01:16:38,694
Go on, beat it.

1468
01:16:38,760 --> 01:16:41,530
Oh, that's just great.

1469
01:16:41,597 --> 01:16:44,366
No, that's fine.

1470
01:16:44,433 --> 01:16:46,902
Oh, shit...

1471
01:16:46,969 --> 01:16:49,838
I didn't know
you were coming over.

1472
01:16:51,039 --> 01:16:52,874
I know.

1473
01:17:02,884 --> 01:17:05,354
[SIGHS]
It's okay.

1474
01:17:10,225 --> 01:17:12,761
[♪♪♪]

1475
01:17:20,869 --> 01:17:23,672
MARY [WHISPERING]:
Look. Ange, look.

1476
01:17:23,739 --> 01:17:25,474
Look.

