01:17:25,540 --> 01:17:28,243
There he is.

1478
01:17:31,980 --> 01:17:35,417
You could say goodbye, Ange.

1479
01:17:35,484 --> 01:17:36,952
What?

1480
01:17:37,019 --> 01:17:39,388
Say goodbye to Rudy now.

1481
01:17:41,423 --> 01:17:43,291
Say goodbye.

1482
01:17:45,694 --> 01:17:47,362
Go on.

1483
01:17:55,771 --> 01:17:59,107
Goodbye, Rudy.

1484
01:17:59,174 --> 01:18:02,310
MARY:
There you go.

1485
01:18:02,377 --> 01:18:04,413
Goodbye, Rudy.

1486
01:18:14,723 --> 01:18:16,925
[SIGHS]

1487
01:18:18,226 --> 01:18:20,395
I'm just gonna stay
a little while, okay?

1488
01:18:20,462 --> 01:18:24,066
It's okay, honey.
You don't have to explain.

1489
01:18:25,434 --> 01:18:27,536
I'll leave
in just a little bit.

1490
01:18:27,602 --> 01:18:30,138
No, shh.

1491
01:18:42,451 --> 01:18:44,986
[♪♪♪]

1492
01:19:01,369 --> 01:19:03,405
Do you want me
to come in?

1493
01:19:03,472 --> 01:19:05,440
No, it's okay.

1494
01:19:08,777 --> 01:19:10,345
Go on home.

1495
01:19:10,412 --> 01:19:13,014
Okay.

1496
01:19:13,081 --> 01:19:14,616
[CAR DOOR CLOSES]

1497
01:19:14,683 --> 01:19:17,152
I'll call you
in the morning.

1498
01:19:17,219 --> 01:19:19,454
Okay.

1499
01:19:19,521 --> 01:19:21,857
Go on, beat it.

1500
01:19:28,563 --> 01:19:31,166
[♪♪♪]

1501
01:20:17,579 --> 01:20:18,847
Who's that?

1502
01:20:18,914 --> 01:20:22,217
It's okay, Pop.
It's just me.

1503
01:20:22,284 --> 01:20:23,852
Oh.

1504
01:20:31,159 --> 01:20:33,528
So did you kill him?

1505
01:20:37,365 --> 01:20:39,134
Yeah.

1506
01:20:40,835 --> 01:20:42,737
I killed him.

1507
01:20:42,804 --> 01:20:45,207
Good.

1508
01:20:48,910 --> 01:20:50,478
I was thinking...

1509
01:20:51,947 --> 01:20:55,617
maybe we ought to clip
someone else too.

1510
01:20:57,419 --> 01:20:59,821
Who was it?

1511
01:20:59,888 --> 01:21:01,790
Go to sleep, Pop.

1512
01:21:01,856 --> 01:21:04,326
I'm so tired.

1513
01:21:10,498 --> 01:21:12,500
What time is it?

1514
01:21:12,567 --> 01:21:14,636
It's late.

1515
01:21:14,703 --> 01:21:16,671
Just go back to sleep.

1516
01:21:16,738 --> 01:21:19,641
I was dreaming.

1517
01:21:23,979 --> 01:21:27,282
I was going somewhere.

1518
01:21:31,753 --> 01:21:33,922
[SNORES]

1519
01:21:37,158 --> 01:21:39,494
[♪♪♪]

1520
01:22:03,051 --> 01:22:05,287
[NO AUDIO]

1521
01:22:20,168 --> 01:22:23,104
[♪♪♪]

1522
01:22:37,485 --> 01:22:38,853
[GUNSHOT]

1523
01:22:38,920 --> 01:22:41,122
[VENTILATOR HISSING]

1524
01:23:22,130 --> 01:23:24,132
[SIGHS]

1525
01:24:06,241 --> 01:24:07,876
Go home, guys.

1526
01:24:07,942 --> 01:24:09,778
Huh?

1527
01:24:09,844 --> 01:24:11,479
Get some rest.

1528
01:24:11,546 --> 01:24:13,214
You sure?

1529
01:24:13,281 --> 01:24:14,849
It's okay?

1530
01:24:14,916 --> 01:24:17,218
Yeah. Go on home.

1531
01:24:17,285 --> 01:24:19,454
Thanks, Ange.

1532
01:24:20,955 --> 01:24:22,991
See you later.

1533
01:24:23,057 --> 01:24:25,460
Yeah, see you later.

1534
01:24:30,131 --> 01:24:32,667
[BIRDS CHIRPING]

1535
01:24:58,660 --> 01:25:00,829
[♪♪♪]

1536
01:25:11,439 --> 01:25:13,508
ANGELO:
I don't know.

1537
01:25:14,576 --> 01:25:17,245
They give you something,

1538
01:25:17,312 --> 01:25:19,814
they take away
something else.

1539
01:25:22,016 --> 01:25:24,219
It's not all one way.

1540
01:25:26,888 --> 01:25:29,390
[♪♪♪]

1541
01:26:00,955 --> 01:26:03,591
[♪♪♪]

